<figureCitation id="13222A4FFFE18B385D64FEC22019FEC2" box="[854,888,336,362]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="33.[189,232,1852,1878]" captionTargetBox="[351,1247,266,1812]" captionTargetId="figure-11@33.[339,1248,265,1815]" captionText="Fig. 6 (part 1). A–I. Male genitalia of Ebenacobius Haran gen. nov., penis in dorsal (left) and lateral (right) view.A. E. curvisetis Haran gen. et sp. nov.B. E. rectirostrisHaran gen. et sp. nov.C. E. duplicatus Haran gen. et sp. nov. D. E. grobbelaarae Haran gen. et sp. nov. E. E. costalis (Fåhraeus, 1844) gen. et comb. nov. F. E. thoracicus Haran gen. et sp. nov. G. E. xhosa Haran gen. et sp. nov. H. E. san Haran gen. et sp. nov. I. E. kuscheli Haran gen. et sp. nov. A–I = not to scale." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6536655" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6536655/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">6C</figureCitation>
